hopobject.body: A few months chlorpromazine thorazine classification Although a highly developed nation, Taiwan offers a picture of what China might be like if it hadn’t become communist, according to Chris Moore, a Taiwan specialist at the tour operator Audley Travel. Traditional culture is less diluted than on the Chinese mainland. “It’s got an off-the-radar quality which appeals to people who have seen a fair bit of the region and are curious about what Taiwan holds,” he says.
